::: HELL BEAST looks to Bright Blade ::: You do show respect....a lesson the 
others could learn from!

::: He walks past her and looks to the view screen, and then to Bright Blade 
still kneeling ::: Tell me a little about yourself.

~~~~~~~~~

::: TRANSANULAS nad OMINOUS rest a moment. They had run from the Predacon 
base, and made it out successfully. Now, they were without a fraction and a 
home. OMINOUS wasnt about to let the spider into his base, so TRANSANULAS was 
preety much on his own. The two argued, and split up. TRANSANULAS head for 
the Maximals to join them, and OMINOUS head for his icy lair to plot the 
demise of his enemies. ::::
